Daryn Hinton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daryn_Hinton 0 Daryn Hinton, born December 28, 1954, is an American former child actress who was raised in the Hollywood entertainment industry in the 1950s and 1960s. Hinton had a spiritual conversion and left the Hollywood connections behind to pursue her newfound faith.
